      },
      "message": "Harden ImageScan command logging\n\nSanitizes the stored `commandLog` channel ID before lookup and resolves it through `ctx.client.channels` so logging works reliably across channel caches. It also guards against non-sendable channels, adds a startup diagnostic log for command log resolution, and improves log payloads with OCR word summaries, clearer field labels, and consistent emoji generation via `String.fromCodePoint`.",
